(14)","guid":"XLo3HDF8aHRjC2RzdR-wnQ","children":[{"id":"155","parent":"154","text":"1. Anticoagulación:","guid":"HJB0MA2Ypbpz01AwVaekcg","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"HNF o HBPM a dosis terapéuticas. Evitar HNF si TIH probable.","guid":"XTYqDC_fCqQeQ6zsC0lNAw","children":[]}]},{"id":"157","parent":"154","text":"2. Glucocorticoides:","guid":"EcSjiwyHEYZQLaKuRbLnKA","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"Metilprednisolona 500-1000 mg IV x 3d, luego prednisona 1 mg/kg/d","guid":"dPZWUV5yOF88OFs4OrmFFg","children":[]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"154","text":"3. Plasmaféresis (5 sesiones) o IgIV (400 mg/kg/d x 5d)","guid":"M2ZOPGFIDyEq9931FJNO5w","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"154","text":"Manejo de soporte:","guid":"AEuphgtKqhsAaLmnL6QSow","children":[{"id":"161","parent":"160","text":"- Hemodiálisis si FRA","guid":"Xw0U9WBTzso36EEie52JJQ","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"160","text":"- Ventilación mecánica si SDRA","guid":"bex0hSu7kVJRRS2XSyKekQ","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"160","text":"- Vasopresores si shock","guid":"W5qb9m-I2oNWa-uUbV8_gQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"164","parent":"149","text":"Segunda línea\\N(casos refractarios):","guid":"fA_sCSaZjkIzEiapcQZCWg","children":[{"id":"165","parent":"164","text":"- Rituximab: 375 mg/m2 semanal x 4 (15)","guid":"BQvGom9KgeErv8dxOHIU3g","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"164","text":"- Eculizumab: 900 mg sem x 4, luego 1200 mg c/2 sem (16)(17)","guid":"UJKRAla3pWZNBWPFLUzIHw","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"164","text":"- Ciclofosfamida (18)(19)","guid":"CDQN2jAQyDgibHi8CH-3YA","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"164","text":"- Sirolimus (20)","guid":"O1tyUyLVMmM4I8oDGmiHSA","children":[]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"149","text":"Ante desencadenante\\Nespecífico:","guid":"AykBLXAMCyUWBhBucRV1sg","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"- Antibióticos ante infección","guid":"G8ecd2dLPgU8OBRDd2I4bg","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"- Interrupción de fármacos sospechosos","guid":"VtQYiRKj_9hkwXfvUuQEkg","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"169","text":"- Considerar parto pretérmino en embarazadas","guid":"OT2OGhfTnplD6kbtPklUvA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"0","text":"Prevención 1ª:","guid":"STWcnF1Jv4IyDbKDY3AUHQ","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"- AAS 81-100 mg/d (3)","guid":"MTQqHhTodUBKul6uCKO5xg","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"- Tratar infecciones precozmente","guid":"Q2t4QWDNZIA_BfslUm-x1g","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"173","text":"- Reducir factores de riesgo: ACO, cirugías electivas (1)(3)","guid":"FVamMEPmjbNokgvmOYn2Pw","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"173","text":"- Tamizaje trombofilias congénitas en embarazadas (24)","guid":"P4KJ21ZlF3MkHvoRft9TYw","children":[]}]},{"id":"178","parent":"0","text":"Prevención 2ª:","guid":"Bx4gem-qDl52u2maV7CxfQ","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"- Warfarina vía oral (INR 2-3) de por vida (1)","guid":"RmGzxEPAzWAE_XmcTpXBng","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"178","text":"- AAS 81-100 mg/d (3)","guid":"c9GVmCdp8lhXFXj-Ly0H7A","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"178","text":"- Evitar suspensiones prolongadas de anticoagulación perioperatoria (21)","guid":"Sj8kuw85QwJJlY80TWgl6A","children":[]}]},{"id":"182","parent":"0","text":"Seguimiento y pronóstico:","guid":"Mh0roSkJRAxcism4SiZQlQ","children":[{"id":"183","parent":"182","text":"- Mortalidad >30% a pesar de terapia agresiva (1)(14)","guid":"f0VOJ1-bn6I-fZubGwzqnw","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"182","text":"- Factores de mal\\Npronóstico (1)(22):","guid":"RubdqHq1r94SbyMNHbr2MQ","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"LES asociado","guid":"DVmvtncwmvxwnvrDRpc90Q","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"184","text":"Compromiso pulmonar y renal","guid":"DwQ5lTSJQbAE4JKNFiJaEA","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"184","text":"Edad >36 años","guid":"JDNQDnub_Cht0wuNapUD0g","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"184","text":"AAF a títulos elevados"